    "Title": "Help Headhunters at ~mission(DefendLocationWrapperLocation)",
    "Description": "Got word that Headhunters ships heading to <EM4>~mission(DefendLocationWrapperLocation|Address)</EM4> are coming under attack. Scans have revealed enemy forces in the wider region intent on targeting our ops. \n\nThere\u2019s enough of them that it\u2019s gonna take more than one person to clear away all that trash. If you can grab your gear and a few friends, I could really use you out there.  \n\nThe specific attack areas and targets are evolving. Don\u2019t worry about the details now. Just get there and I\u2019ll let you know where you\u2019re needed.  \n\nHandle this right and I\u2019ll give the main contractor a bonus <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4>.\n\n- Stows",
